      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄭風·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有女同車.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有女同車，顏如舜華，將翱將翔，佩玉瓊琚，彼美孟姜，洵美且都。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is the lady in the carriage [with him],
With the countenance like the flower of the ephemeral hedge-tree.
As they move about,
The beautiful Ju-gems of her girdle-pendant appear.
That beautiful eldest Jiang,
Is truly admirable and elegant.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
