      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄭風·009.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有女同車.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有女同行，顏如舜英，將翱將翔，佩玉將將，彼美孟姜，德音不忘。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>There is the young lady walking [with him],
With a countenance like the ephemeral blossoms of the hedge-tree.
As they move about,
The gems of her girdle-pendant tinkle.
Of that beautiful eldest Jiang,
The virtuous fame is not to be forgotten.</seg>
      </tuv>
